*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.p12
*.pfx
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
id_ecdsa*
**/.ssh/

# API keys and credential files
**/credentials.json
**/service-account*.json
**/auth.json
**/*-credentials.*
**/*-secrets.*
**/*-keys.*

# Database connection strings and configs
**/database.ini
**/db.conf
**/connection.conf

